title: lord of the rings battle for middle earth 2 all maps pack
description:
this are all maps i could find on internet. Enjoy!

Instructions:

-1. Go to start

-2. Choose Run.

-3. Type: "%appdata%My Battle for Middle-earth Files/Maps" NOTE: This is the English version!, If you have another language game you need to do it different..)

-4. A new window will open and there you see the "User maps" you got from multiplayer games, or you had already installed.

-5. Unzip your map, copy and past it into the new window.

-6.(For other language players only). Type: "%appdata%". Now see if you can find a folder with Battle for Middle Earth in the name. Then go maps and copy and paste the map in it.
